TEXT.S: = Isawalian pahikukian = Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Ciansyang ka alang Isawalian pahikukian. 972 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 2,516 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 26% niqan 646 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 74% niqan 1,870 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Amis 18%, Tayal 1%, Bunun 1%.
